                </blockquote>
                <h2>Little bit about me</h2>
                <p> I study Communication &amp; Multimedia Design at the University of Applied Sciences Amsterdam and in my free time I love playing videogames, occasionally making drawings and digitizing them. I'm also a huuuuge Star Wars fan (and several other science-fictions)</p>
                <p> The two traits that define me is being annoyingly organised and being a perfectionist. I like to make a plan that is well structured in order to achieve a goal that has been set, but i’m also flexible enough to adjust this plan if necessary. Because I’m a perfectionist I don’t stop until I’m satisfied with my work and I always aim for something better so that I can outdo myself. </p>
